343
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,440
Prepare a gift for me.

344
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:12,240
I'll go pay my respects.

345
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,440
You lose.

346
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:20,320
Drink.

347
00:22:22,840 --> 00:22:23,560
Fine.

348
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:24,820
I'm not scared.

349
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:46,800
Drink.

350
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:52,120
