353
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,880
It's boring.

354
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,680
Are you jealous?

355
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,120
Jealous of whom?

356
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,560
Stop pretending.

357
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,360
Xie Liangchen and Shen Junshan

358
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:13,960
went missing for days

359
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,530
and came back together.

360
00:23:16,280 --> 00:23:18,680
You just came out from the hospital, right?

361
00:23:29,280 --> 00:23:30,810
Don't be upset, Gu Yanzhen.

362
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:34,000
Clearly, we're both fools.

363
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,800
Here, to two fools.

364
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:36,560
Cheers!

365
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,160
Who is a fool?

366
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:40,960
Me.

367
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,800
I'm a fool.

368
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,120
Why do I feel you said that to me?

369
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:48,600
No.

370
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,250
I was talking to myself.

371
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:53,020
Actually, things aren't what you think.

372
00:23:54,080 --> 00:23:55,340
Then tell me the truth.

373
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:03,900
Never mind.

374
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,540
What are you doing?

375
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:07,720
Don't leave me hanging.

376
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,370
You have a big mouth.

377
00:24:11,520 --> 00:24:12,680
What did you say?

378
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:14,900
Who has a big mouth?

379
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:17,800
Gu Yanzhen.

380
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:18,880
Sit back.

381
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,000
Miss. Qu.

382
00:24:23,800 --> 00:24:24,800
Stop right there!

383
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,000
Stop now!

384
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:28,720
Stop right there…

385
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:32,680
Blood!

386
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:33,740
Somebody help!

387
00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:35,220
What did you do?

388
00:24:36,560 --> 00:24:37,240
I...

389
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,000
I don't look good.

390
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:40,560
