393
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,600
Doctor.

394
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:24,080
Doctor, how is he?

395
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,960
He's still unconscious.

396
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,420
We gave him four stitches.

397
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:28,720
Right now,

398
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,920
he's stable.

399
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,040
He's fine. He's OK. Don't worry.

400
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:33,100
Is his life at risk?

401
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,130
I don't think so.

402
00:25:34,320 --> 00:25:35,560
When will he wake up?

403
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:36,600
He'll

404
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:39,570
wake up tomorrow morning at the earliest.

405
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:41,420
Thank you, doctor.

406
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:48,880
I'm sorry.

407
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,960
We'll pay for his medical bills.

408
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,280
Who wants your money?

409
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:55,240
If anything happens to my husband,

410
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,520
I'll destroy you.

411
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:58,200
The doctor said he's fine.

412
00:25:58,320 --> 00:26:00,040
That's his opinion.

413
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,760
My husband's head is injured.

414
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:03,960
What if he becomes a fool,

415
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:06,160
he loses his mind or becomes paralyzed?

416
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:08,000
Who will support our whole family?

417
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,120
Who will take the responsibility?

418
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:10,000
Stop yelling.

419
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:11,280
Are you done?

420
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:12,680
The doctor said he's stable.

421
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:14,040
Why are you cursing your husband?

422
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,600
You...

423
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:16,980
This is a hospital.

424
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:18,700
Bring your argument outside.

425
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,500
I'm telling you

426
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:23,920
this isn't over.

427
00:26:28,080 --> 00:26:29,160
Ridiculous!

428
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,520
What a shrew!

429
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:34,280
You're no better yourself.

430
00:26:34,280 --> 00:26:35,560
It was his fault.

431
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:36,840
You shouldn't have hit him.

432
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,040
He took photos of me.

433
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:39,840
Aren't you a star?

434
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:40,920
A photo can't kill you.

435
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:42,520
Stars also have rights.

436
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:44,640
He didn't ask for my permission.

437
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:46,090
Look at my dark circles.

438
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:47,560
I haven't slept well for days.

439
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:48,480
They're huge!

440
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,480
My skin looks bad.

441
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,680
My clothes are dirty.

442
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:51,720
My hair is greasy.

443
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,480
What would people think if they saw me like this?

444
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,160
This face is my meal ticket, got it?

445
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,200
So you hit him.

446
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,440
What if he sues you?

447
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:00,280
I'd rather be sued

448
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:01,960
than have that photo leaked out.

449
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,220
I don't understand what you girls think.

450
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:05,960
You know nothing.

451
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:12,320
Gu Yanzhen.

452
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:29,360
I have something to tell you.

453
00:27:30,280 --> 00:27:31,280
So do I.

454
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:32,640
I’ll go first.

455
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:34,600
I was

456
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:35,960
angry earlier today,

457
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,760
but now I'm fine.

458
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:41,200
It's over.

459
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,140
I'm not angry anymore.

460
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:45,290
But you must stay away from him.

461
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:47,560
I won't forgive you so easily next time.

462
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:50,760
What...what are you talking about?

463
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,640
I'm done. Your turn.

464
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,400
After you left today,

465
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:58,880
I lost something.

466
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,280
I want to ask you about it.

467
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:04,540
What are you implying?

468
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,860
Are you calling me a thief?

469
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:07,840
No.

470
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:09,560
I just want to ask if you saw it.

471
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:10,880
It's a yellow bag.

472
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:12,080
Shen Junshan and I

473
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:13,440
took it from the Japanese.

474
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:13,840
It's important.

475
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:14,700
I didn't see it.

476
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,520
Why are you still here?

477
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:41,650
I'm waiting for you.

478
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,760
I knew Xie Liangchen

479
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:43,880
would kick you out.

480
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:46,420
You two argued?

481
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:48,720
Given your look,

482
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,000
I can tell that

483
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:52,480
You're the only one in love.

484
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,320
Unrequited love.

485
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:54,320
You're lovesick.

486
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:55,480
Are you done?

487
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,160
Not yet.

488
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:59,080
How about I give you a tip?

489
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:01,440
You want it?

490
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:03,120
Shoot.

491
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,240
Look at you,

492
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:09,760
you've always been clinging onto her.

493
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:10,960
When she went back to Peking,

494
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,220
you followed her back.

495
00:29:13,080 --> 00:29:14,340
When she was in danger,

496
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,840
you left your engagement and came back

497
00:29:15,840 --> 00:29:16,880
to protect her.

498
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,760
So tedious!

499
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:21,040
If it were me,

500
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:22,640
I wouldn't like you, either.

501
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,050
Not challenging at all.

502
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,040
You do have a point.

503
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:30,880
Am I right?

504
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,840
Then what should I do?

505
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,410
Should I ignore her?

506
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:37,600
You're wrong.

507
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:39,460
Competition promotes progress.

508
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:43,000
You should find a girlfriend

509
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:44,960
and do PDA in front of her every day

510
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:46,080
to make her jealous.

511
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:47,480
Then she'll get anxious.

512
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,860
Easier said than done.

513
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:51,210
If you can't find a girlfriend,

514
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:53,520
I can help you.

515
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:56,120
You?

516
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,160
Forget it.

517
00:29:59,000 --> 00:29:59,640
What?

518
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:00,690
Gu Yanzhen, I...

519
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,240
I'm serious.

520
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,720
Just think about it.

521
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,240
I'm a superstar.

522
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,400
No thanks.

523
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:11,920
When Jin Xianrong comes to visit Shen Junshan next time,

524
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,960
keep an eye on her.

525
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:16,360
Only you guys have come here.

526
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:17,680
Others are all clean.

527
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:19,010
She's the only one left.

528
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:19,720
Besides,

529
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:20,720
my gut tells me

530
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:21,980
that woman is bad news.

531
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,930
Are you sure you don't need my help?

532
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,440
No, thanks. Go back.

533
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,880
So ungrateful.

534
00:30:59,000 --> 00:30:59,680
Mom.

535
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:05,440
Sorry for troubling you tonight.

536
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,640
I shall take my leave.

537
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:08,600
I failed to discipline her.

538
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:10,600
I apologize for causing you trouble.

539
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,680
When you return,

540
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:14,160
do apologize to Vice Minister Gu for me.

541
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,480
You're too kind.

542
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:16,240
OK.

543
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,880
I'll visit him myself later.

544
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:27,980
You troublemaker!

545
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,960
You still remember to come back.

546
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:30,800
Have you eaten?

547
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:31,480
I have.

548
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,440
Who is that man?

549
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,560
You dare ask!

550
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,440
You brought shame to our whole family.

551
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:41,480
It's not all Manting's fault.

552
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:43,340
It's not hers, then is it my fault?

553
00:31:44,560 --> 00:31:45,600
A young lady

554
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:48,480
stole another girl's fiance during their engagement.

555
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,440
It's shameful, don't you know?

556
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,720
I'm not a lady anyway.

557
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,360
Dad, you're right.

558
00:31:54,360 --> 00:31:55,720
I'm just a showgirl.

559
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:56,440
You...

560
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:57,660
You dare talk back!

561
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,360
Forget it.

562
00:31:58,720 --> 00:32:00,040
Don't upset yourself.

563
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:01,360
Come on.

564
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:02,620
Apologize to your dad.

565
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:09,560
I don't like what Mr. Zhu said.

566
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,920
He made it look like

567
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:12,200
that Gu Yanzhen

568
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,600
had nothing to do with it.

569
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:16,320
Don't you know your own daughter?

570
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:18,160
She's spoiled,

571
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:20,600
but I don't believe she'd steal

572
00:32:21,040 --> 00:32:22,970
other people's fiance on purpose.

573
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:25,680
What have I done to have such a daughter?

574
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:29,000
I don't want a dictator to be my dad, either.

575
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:30,530
What did you say?

576
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,840
Where are you going now?

577
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:01,360
Shen Junshan.

578
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:04,200
Hi there.

579
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:06,720
Hi, Xianrong.

580
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:08,180
I just arrived.

581
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,480
How are you doing?

582
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:14,010
Much better.

583
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:17,060
I may be able to get discharged tomorrow.

584
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,360
What's with the rush?

585
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,140
You should stay and rest more.

586
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:21,650
It's just a scratch.

587
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,730
No need to stay here any longer.

588
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:26,280
I envy you.

589
00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:27,410
I want to leave, too,

590
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:29,260
but the doctor doesn't let me.

591
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:30,960
Your leg is wounded.

592
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,530
Bed rest is good for you.

593
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:35,010
Moving around may slow down your healing.

594
00:33:36,080 --> 00:33:37,120
I'm in a wheelchair.

595
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:37,920
It's fine.

596
00:33:38,760 --> 00:33:40,560
I'm almost bored to death.

597
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,160
Let me.

598
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,760
Your hand is injured.

599
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:53,800
I can do it.

600
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:54,720
It's OK.

601
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:55,920
Let me.

602
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,120
I can do it myself.

603
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,400
Junshan,

604
00:34:09,670 --> 00:34:10,670
you want a banana?

605
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:11,560
No thanks.

606
00:34:14,040 --> 00:34:15,480
And you, Liangchen?

607
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:17,880
Sure.

608
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:21,280
Thank you.

609
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:29,120
Why do you have callus on your palm?

610
00:34:29,520 --> 00:34:30,780
You practiced kung fu?

611
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:34,639
I know nothing about kung fu.

612
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:36,219
I got it from doing chores.

613
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,080
Really?

614
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:38,840
I thought

615
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,290
only sabers could leave that mark.

616
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:43,440
You're wrong.

617
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:46,760
Probably.

618
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:48,320
People use guns now.

619
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,659
Few people use sabers.

620
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:50,600
At our Academy,

621
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:52,600
we only have one saber skill course.

622
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:07,100
I heard you just came to China.

623
00:35:07,160 --> 00:35:07,880
May I ask

624
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,340
Where're you from?

625
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,000
Britain.

626
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,080
Which city?

627
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:11,960
Liverpool.

628
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,280
A city or arts.

629
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,410
No wonder you look so artsy.

630
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,000
Thank you.

631
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:23,920
Do you have relatives here?

632
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:25,280
I do.

633
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:26,760
Really?

634
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,720
We've known each other for a while.

635
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:30,580
I still don't know where you live.

636
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:31,400
Perhaps

637
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,000
we can go visit you sometime.

638
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:37,160
Junshan hasn't been to my place yet.

639
00:35:37,520 --> 00:35:39,120
He never even asked about it.

640
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:41,610
You've asked me so many questions.

641
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,320
May I assume that

642
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,680
you have a crush on me?

643
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:47,760
You must be joking.

644
00:35:49,640 --> 00:35:51,240
Actually, I am.

645
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:53,280
But I have to warn you

646
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,280
not to fall in love with me,

647
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:58,360
because I'm already in love with someone else.

648
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:11,920
You guys talk.

649
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:12,850
I need to go back.

650
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,120
Do you need help?

651
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,000
No need.

652
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:16,860
I have Xiaojun.

653
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,960
Take care.

654
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:39,440
Why do I sense

655
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,330
hostility between you two?

656
00:36:42,600 --> 00:36:43,160
Really?

657
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:46,090
I feel Liangchen and I are getting along well.

658
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:07,360
How did it go?

659
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:08,700
Did you ask her?

660
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,360
What should I say?

661
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,520
If she didn't take it,

662
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,080
she'd feel offended.

663
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,520
If she did take it,

664
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:16,780
she wouldn't admit it.

665
00:37:19,720 --> 00:37:20,960
So our hands are tied.

666
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:23,840
I still think she's odd.

667
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,320
Why?

668
00:37:25,520 --> 00:37:26,320
Just a hunch.

669
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,800
It can be wrong.

670
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:31,680
Take your time.

671
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:32,610
I need to go home.

672
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:34,120
You don't need to come this afternoon.

673
00:37:34,120 --> 00:37:35,360
I'll ask the nurse to bring me lunch.

674
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,920
You've been absent from school for days.

675
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,280
I don't have any class.

676
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:40,480
Students are all busy with speeches.

677
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,480
When Gu Yanzhen comes,

678
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,740
tell him to be careful.

679
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,380
His dad is the negotiator.

680
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:46,160
Students all know his name.

681
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,780
If the negotiation fails,

682
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:49,290
he'll be in trouble.

683
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:50,440
I will.

684
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:51,400
See you.

685
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:52,800
Bye.

686
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:10,800
Hi, Xianrong.

687
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:13,520
Xie Liangchen.

688
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,200
Liangchen,

689
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,770
what are you doing here?

690
00:38:20,640 --> 00:38:21,840
I need some fresh air.

691
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,160
Are you alone?

692
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,520
My friend went home.

693
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,290
Are you leaving?

694
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,760
Xianrong,

695
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,480
could you do me a favor?

696
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,880
The water is cold.

697
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:36,090
Can you bring me some hot water?

698
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,040
Sure.

699
00:38:44,520 --> 00:38:46,520
You're skilled, Xianrong.

700
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,960
I have no skills.

701
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,420
I'm just flexible.

702
00:38:57,640 --> 00:38:59,880
Why do you have callus on your palm?

703
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,260
You practiced kung fu?

704
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,400
I know nothing about kung fu.

705
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,160
I got it from doing chores.

706
00:39:05,640 --> 00:39:06,840
I thought

707
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:08,970
only sabers could leave that mark.

708
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:11,000
You're wrong.

709
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,400
Ms. Huo.

710
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:13,780
Well, it's not her.

711
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:16,410
Gu Yanzhen and Shen Junshan wouldn't take it.

712
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:18,120
That leaves Jin Xianrong.

713
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:24,800
Hold it tight.

714
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,570
Don't drop it again.

715
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:28,120
Thank you.

716
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:30,240
I'm leaving then.

717
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:31,160
Bye.

718
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:50,210
Why didn't you tell me about the shooting?

719
00:39:50,480 --> 00:39:51,880
What have you been doing?

720
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:56,890
When the shooting began, you were in Nanjing.

721
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,680
I couldn't reach you.

722
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,640
It's been a while since I came back.

723
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:01,900
You should've told me.

724
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:07,360
Manting,

725
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,680
it's not just this movie.

726
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,560
All your work has been

727
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:21,580
canceled except for your show in Paramo.

728
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,480
What did you say?

729
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:38,800
Mr. Duan has terminated your contract.

730
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:41,380
Your dad signed it for you.

731
00:40:48,720 --> 00:40:49,400
Manting,

732
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:52,380
you know my situation.

733
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,960
My whole family is counting on me.

734
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:58,280
Mr. Duan

735
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:02,090
has reassigned me to Pingting.

736
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:05,800
Yang's with her now.

737
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:09,640
I know

738
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:12,000
leaving you right now

739
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,920
isn't right,

740
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:18,160
plus, you've always been good to me.

741
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:21,730
But my mom's in poor health.

742
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:27,530
I have no choice.

743
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,640
I'm sorry.
